project: Yay, you made it! Now you can annoy your loved one with your silly and goofy existence!

Oh no! You appear to be stuck in a nightmare! You got lost in a spooky scary dreamscape maze, crawled with creepy eyeballs! But fear not, at the end of the maze, your entitled significant other awaits with his calming presence! Navigate through the maze to reach your beloved, but be careful not to get caught by the floating eyes, for they will drive you mad!
